WEBVTT

00:00.041 --> 00:04.001
<b></b>June 15

00:10.931 --> 00:13.971
<b>The asphalt burns 
and sweat oozes out of every pore</b>

00:14.301 --> 00:16.931
<b>as the blazing sun saps your energy away.</b>

00:16.931 --> 00:19.231
<b>I get it. I feel your pain.</b>

00:19.541 --> 00:21.611
<b>I'm in sales, too, after all.</b>

00:21.611 --> 00:23.331
<b>But I must apologize.</b>

00:23.331 --> 00:27.931
<b>My words of empathy, spoken in the 
chilly confines of this smoking room,</b>

00:27.931 --> 00:31.441
<b>hold no water at all, and I know that.</b>

00:37.241 --> 00:39.411
<b>This little act isn't helping.</b>

00:42.331 --> 00:59.681
<b>Out of Order</b>

00:42.331 --> 00:46.091
<b>Why is the damn A/C out of order?!</b>

00:46.091 --> 00:48.011
<b>This must be part 
of the chief's master plan!</b>

00:48.011 --> 00:51.401
<b>He probably jammed 
one of his things inside the A/C!</b>

00:51.401 --> 00:53.611
<b>It's basically summer! It's hot!</b>

00:51.401 --> 00:54.451
<b>He can't be that bored.</b>

00:53.611 --> 00:56.391
<b>What, it's so hot, it's shot?!</b>

00:54.451 --> 00:57.801
<b>Don't get so heated. 
You'll only feel the heat.</b>

00:56.391 --> 00:58.641
<b>That's a shitty joke, 
and my take is freezing cold!</b>

00:57.801 --> 00:59.681
<b>Oh, fine.</b>

00:58.641 --> 01:01.761
<b>Wait, that'd be perfect, 
but it's not cold at all!</b>

01:00.041 --> 01:01.781
<b><i>It'll get fixed tomorrow.</i></b>

01:01.781 --> 01:04.171
<b>If anything, it's hot! 
This is pissing me off!</b>

01:01.781 --> 01:03.241
<b><i>It'll get fixed next week.</i></b>

01:03.241 --> 01:05.191
<b><i>It'll stay like this all summer.</i></b>

01:07.131 --> 01:07.941
<b>Oh?</b>

01:08.291 --> 01:11.321
<b>Good news, Suzuki. 
It'll get fixed tomorrow.</b>

01:11.321 --> 01:13.411
<b>What? How would you know that?</b>

01:13.411 --> 01:17.451
<b>My little superstition. 
It's pretty accurate, you know?</b>

01:19.551 --> 01:21.821
<b>Squee! I'm tickled pink to hear that!</b>

01:22.211 --> 01:25.081
<b>If it's not fixed tomorrow, 
you're a dead man!</b>

01:25.081 --> 01:26.291
<b>Now, now.</b>

01:26.631 --> 01:29.101
<b>Just believe in me and wait, Suzuki-san.</b>

01:29.101 --> 01:31.881
<b>A cool future is nearly upon us.</b>

01:33.561 --> 01:34.321
<b>Urk.</b>

01:35.181 --> 01:37.291
<b>G-Good evening.</b>

01:40.461 --> 01:41.601
<b>My bad.</b>

01:41.601 --> 01:44.011
<b>I was washing away some milk 
a driver spilled everywhere</b>

01:44.011 --> 01:45.521
<b>and started enjoying it too much.</b>

01:47.201 --> 01:49.641
<b>A hose is a mighty tempting plaything.</b>

03:31.681 --> 03:34.261
<b><i>This is weirdly tense.</i></b>

03:34.931 --> 03:37.861
<b>Thank you for lending me 
the towel and trousers.</b>

03:38.301 --> 03:40.531
<b>It's the least I could do, 
since it was my fault.</b>

03:40.531 --> 03:42.011
<b>Oh, not at all.</b>

03:44.611 --> 03:47.751
<b>No need to be so formal, Sasaki-kun.</b>

03:48.221 --> 03:50.101
<b>We're pretty close in age.</b>

03:51.591 --> 03:53.151
<b>W-We are?!</b>

03:53.501 --> 03:56.401
<b>You look like you're in your forties.</b>

03:56.401 --> 03:59.531
<b>And I'm forty exactly. 
Let's keep it casual.</b>

03:59.891 --> 04:04.361
<b>Someone around my age is heading the 
busiest supermarket around these parts?</b>

04:04.361 --> 04:06.011
<b>You have my utmost respect.</b>

04:06.011 --> 04:09.041
<b><i>Why'd that make you up the formality?</i></b>

04:09.441 --> 04:13.301
<b>You must be impressed every time 
you learn a person's age.</b>

04:17.331 --> 04:20.801
<b>I can only imagine how you reacted 
when you learned Tayama's.</b>

04:20.801 --> 04:23.551
<b>Huh? Tayama-san's age?</b>

04:27.711 --> 04:28.811
<b>Yeah.</b>

04:29.531 --> 04:31.541
<b>I have no idea.</b>

04:33.111 --> 04:35.591
<b>Don't you smoke together all the time?</b>

04:35.591 --> 04:37.191
<b>Y-Yeah.</b>

04:37.561 --> 04:40.111
<b>You don't ask her any personal questions?</b>

04:40.111 --> 04:41.221
<b>I don't.</b>

04:41.221 --> 04:43.771
<b>Do you just have no interest in people?</b>

04:43.771 --> 04:44.581
<b>Huh?</b>

04:46.091 --> 04:48.481
<b>Of course I'm interested.</b>

04:53.091 --> 04:55.461
<b>While she messes with me at times,</b>

04:55.891 --> 04:59.091
<b>she still talks to an old dude like me.</b>

04:59.741 --> 05:03.181
<b>How could I <i>not</i> want 
to get to know her better?</b>

05:05.351 --> 05:10.171
<b>But I enjoy just listening to the things 
she wants to talk about.</b>

05:19.851 --> 05:24.701
<b>The rest I can just wonder 
about as I walk home.</b>

05:26.081 --> 05:28.461
<b><i>No wonder she took to him.</i></b>

05:29.991 --> 05:31.331
<b>I get it now.</b>

05:32.011 --> 05:34.921
<b>So you're saying you <i>do</i> like Tayama-san?</b>

05:34.921 --> 05:37.241
<b>Whoa! Can we not jump to conclusions?!</b>

05:37.241 --> 05:38.131
<b>Do you hate her, then?</b>

05:38.391 --> 05:40.011
<b>You know I don't!</b>

05:40.371 --> 05:42.201
<b>Then what exactly is it?</b>

05:42.201 --> 05:44.141
<b>I mean, of course I lik...</b>

05:44.141 --> 05:46.371
<b>Heya, I dropped by after a shopping trip.</b>

05:54.621 --> 05:55.461
<b>Hmm?</b>

05:57.061 --> 05:57.841
<b>Tch.</b>

05:59.151 --> 06:03.191
<b>I'm sorry, Sasaki-kun. I've been summoned 
to deal with a customer complaint.</b>

06:04.291 --> 06:06.621
<b>I'll be back with money 
to pay for your dry cleaning.</b>

06:06.621 --> 06:08.281
<b>Have a chat with Tayama in the meantime.</b>

06:08.281 --> 06:10.791
<b>Oh, okay...</b>

06:10.791 --> 06:12.351
<b>Bye.</b>

06:18.091 --> 06:20.551
<b>You're soaked, Sasaki-san.</b>

06:20.551 --> 06:24.431
<b>Oh, yeah, I had a little accident.</b>

06:24.771 --> 06:25.971
<b>Huh...</b>

06:36.851 --> 06:39.281
<b>By the way, uh, Tayama-san?</b>

06:39.281 --> 06:41.191
<b>Did you hear all that?</b>

06:41.991 --> 06:43.441
<b>Hear all what?</b>

06:45.051 --> 06:48.041
<b>Nothing. It was no big deal.</b>

06:48.041 --> 06:50.951
<b>Your manager and I 
were just making small talk—</b>

06:52.931 --> 06:54.971
<b>Wait, what? T-Tayama-san?</b>

06:54.971 --> 06:57.461
<b>You need to dry your hair.</b>

06:57.461 --> 07:00.211
<b>Uh, I didn't get my head wet...</b>

07:01.721 --> 07:03.141
<b>Twenty-four.</b>

07:07.631 --> 07:08.471
<b>Wh...</b>

07:09.011 --> 07:11.451
<b>What is that number?</b>

07:12.891 --> 07:17.981
<b>You can wonder about that 
as you walk home.</b>

07:21.731 --> 07:25.361
<b>Translation: Sriram Gurunathan</b>

07:25.861 --> 07:29.491
<b>Editing & Typesetting: Geoff Mazzolini
Subtitle Timing: Krzysztof Kunc</b>

07:30.201 --> 07:33.451
<b>Quality Check: Zachary Carlysle
Translation Check: Sho Stifler</b>
